# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CHARBUCKS POS — Frontend Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and update the values.
#
# SCENARIO 1: Frontend on SAME machine as backend
#   Leave this blank or comment it out — the Vite proxy
#   will forward /api calls to localhost:3000 automatically.
#
# SCENARIO 2: Frontend on a DIFFERENT machine
#   Set this to the backend machine's IP address:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:3000/api
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:3000/api
